00:29:38.159 --> 00:29:39.990
It almost ripped

00:29:40.000 --> 00:29:42.230
her arm out

00:29:42.240 --> 00:29:43.909
of the socket and

00:29:45.200 --> 00:29:47.830
completely off her body.

00:29:51.600 --> 00:29:53.990
After

00:29:54.000 --> 00:29:55.590
seven surgeries, she could not lift her

00:29:55.600 --> 00:29:58.149
hand above her head, but by the

00:29:58.159 --> 00:29:59.510
power of God, she was raising her

00:29:59.520 --> 00:30:03.830
hand in church. It

00:30:03.840 --> 00:30:06.470
was amazing to see an arm that

00:30:06.480 --> 00:30:09.750
was almost completely ripped off.

00:30:09.760 --> 00:30:11.909
God is so good; it is just the

00:30:11.919 --> 00:30:13.990
beginning.

00:30:14.000 --> 00:30:17.430
We

00:30:17.440 --> 00:30:20.070
stand by Jesus the healer,

00:30:20.080 --> 00:30:22.149
the same yesterday, today, and

00:30:22.159 --> 00:30:24.470
forever.

00:30:29.679 --> 00:30:32.070
Thank you for joining us

00:30:32.080 --> 00:30:34.070
today.

00:30:34.080 --> 00:30:36.950
We

00:30:36.960 --> 00:30:39.750
hope it blessed you. This

00:30:39.760 --> 00:30:41.430
is stuff that we needed to say

00:30:41.430 --> 00:30:41.440
and

00:30:41.440 --> 00:30:43.590
pray. That prayer

00:30:43.590 --> 00:30:43.600
for Kari

00:30:43.600 --> 00:30:45.110
Lake

00:30:45.120 --> 00:30:47.430
was

00:30:47.440 --> 00:30:50.070
definitely necessary.

00:30:55.360 --> 00:30:57.029
Put a smile on your face and a song

00:30:57.039 --> 00:30:59.669
in your heart. Jesus loves you,

00:30:59.679 --> 00:31:01.590
and we love you.

